        </bcl:paragraph>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e799">
        <bcl:num>9</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>For the purposes of section 2 (2) (t) of the Act, collecting trade accounts
          receivable from non-resident persons is a prescribed financial activity of a
          corporation.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:hnote>[en. B.C. Reg. 528/2004; am. B.C. Regs. 210/2006; 138/2008, s. 2; 186/2008, s. 1;
        188/2010, s. 4; 370/2012.]</bcl:hnote>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e813">
      <bcl:marginalnote>International financial activity — patents</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>5</bcl:num>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e821">
        <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
